title: Jason Brice [2008] [L169-DBT]cbr
description:
When reading one day, Alcante learns by chance that a novelist "predicted" the Titanic disaster fourteen years before the event - for real! What if this same author had, in another book, predicted the death of one of his readers? What if, in the only copy of this book, the exact page on which the murderer's name is revealed is missing? What if, what if, what if...? 

enjoy
happy holidays
